Package org.eclipselabs.emfpath.exception

Exception Summary
EMFPathException Default abstract EMFPath Exception
NoSuchFeatureException A exception that occurs when a EStructuralFeature is not found in an EClass or its superclasses.
NotFoundException A NotFoundException is an EMFPath specific exception to force users to handle possible null returned values.
